These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, russian, indian, dutch
4 different pets are kept: rat, hedgehog, chinchilla, guinea-pig
There 4 different types of food: mango, pumpkin, watermelon, blueberry
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, jet-ski, motorbike, taxi
 1. the person eating pumpkin is not to the right of the person eating mango##8
 2. the person driving the airplane is not to the left of the person driving the airplane##8
 3. the person driving the taxi is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person eating mango is not to the left of the person eating blueberry##8
 5. the person driving the airplane is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
 7. the russian is somewhere to the right of the nigerian##5
 8. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person eating pumpkin##2
 9. the person driving the taxi is the owner of the chinchilla##1
10. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the dutch##1
11. the indian is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
12. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the russian##5
13. the owner of the chinchilla is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
14. the russian is the person driving the motorbike##1
15. the russian is not the person eating pumpkin##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Nationality         | nigerian     | russian   | dutch | indian |
| Pet   | hedgehog | guinea-pig   | rat   | chinchilla  |
| Food         | pumpkin  | watermelon  | blueberry  | mango |
| Transport     | airplane    | motorbike | jet-ski     | taxi    |

