.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, baking, chess, rock-climbing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, weightlifting, rowing, lacrosse
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, indie, salsa, trance
House: cottage, palace, gothic-revival, tower
 1. the fan of salsa is between the cottage house and the fan of indie##2
 2. the person who's hobby is baking is not to the right of the palace house##8
 3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
 4. the person who's hobby is photography is not to the right of the tower house##8
 5. the cottage house is not to the left of the fan of indie##8
 6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##8
 7. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the left of the tower house##5
 8. the gothic-revival house is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of house is the palace house##1
10. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the cottage house##3
11. the cottage house is not to the left of the fan of salsa##8
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
13. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
14. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
15. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
17. the person who's hobby is photography is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
18. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the right of the palace house##8
19. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Hobby      | photography | chess | rock-climbing  | baking  |
| Sport          | lacrosse     | weightlifting | basketball | rowing  |
| Music-Genre   | indie    | salsa  | trance | house |
| House           | gothic-revival | tower | cottage    | palace  |

