House: townhouse, modern, palace, ranch-style
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, onion, avocado, cherry
4 different games are played: backgammon, poker, chess, monopoly
 1. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 2. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the ranch-style house##5
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the person eating cabbage##5
 5. the person playing chess is not to the right of the townhouse house##8
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the palace house##8
 7. the person eating avocado is in an odd position##4
 8. the palace house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 9. the ranch-style house is on the left of the modern house##1
10. the person playing poker is on the far right##1
11. the townhouse house is not to the left of the person eating onion##8
12. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | camping    | sudoku   | skydiving | card-games |
| House   | townhouse     | palace  | ranch-style   | modern      |
| Food   | onion | cabbage    | avocado      | cherry       |
| Game         | chess    | backgammon | monopoly   | poker    |

