 3. the person eating plum is the bongani-smoker##1
 4. the person eating banana is between the blend-smoker and the aristoff-smoker##2
 5. the wooden house is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in december is not to the right of the person eating banana##8
 7. the tower house is in an odd position##4
 8. the wooden house is somewhere to the right of the futuristic house##5
 9. the tower house is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
10. the aristoff-smoker is the person who's birthday is in december##1
11. the person who's birthday is in july is not to the right of the person eating apple##8
12. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
13. the wooden house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
14. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
15. the futuristic house is in an odd position##4

