 4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 5. the person driving the bike is not to the right of the baccarat-smoker##8
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the right of the person driving the bike##8
 7. the person who's sport is handball is not to the left of the person traveling to liverpool##8
 8. the chaman-smoker is the person driving the trike##1
 9. the dannemann-smoker is not to the left of the person traveling to new-york##8
10. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the left of the person driving the bike##8
11. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person traveling to new-york and the person driving the trike##2
12. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
13. the chaman-smoker is not to the right of the person driving the trike##8
14. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3

.:: Answer ::.
