 8. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
10. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
11. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
13. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the left of the owner of the cat##8
14. the owner of the rat is not to the right of the owner of the dog##8
15. the owner of the rat is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
16. the owner of the hamster is not to the right of the person watching western movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3     |    4    |
| Pet           | hamster | rat       | cat      | dog  |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | martial-arts | western   | drama   |
| Birthday   | october   | september          | december      | may  |
| Hobby   | dancing   | hiking      | gardening | collecting |

